data.description: This beautifully remodeled 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath home is a testament to modern elegance and country quietude. The open concept living room and dining room features a gorgeous whitewashed fireplace with updated built-in cabinetry. The home offers 3 bedrooms that have been freshly painted along with new trim and paint throughout the entire house. The main bathroom has been completely remodeled and the half bath has been updated. Outside, step into your own country paradise with a large backyard with wooded landscaping. Enjoy the natural beauty of the surroundings and the quiet serenity of this neighborhood. Located in Midwest City with easy access to local parks, schools and shops. Located in Midwest City, but the schools are Choctaw and Nicoma Park. Schedule a viewing today and start living the life you've always dreamed of! List of updates included. Back on the market due to no fault of the seller.
